到警察行過, 我都會好羨慕佢地, 可以做到, 我做唔到既夢想<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n考特區公安駛撚學歷咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84d3c135b64435c0722d236c467614581ac1f136","tid":125221,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T13:40:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「道德危機」( Moral Hazard）理論<br />\n<br />\n「道德危機」原本是保險業的理論：當合約的其中一方完全不用承擔違約的後果時，就會改採取對自身利益最大化的自私行為。<br />\n<br />\n換句話說，黑警完全不用承擔違返法律的後果時 (如可以獲得鉅額金錢抵消入獄的損失、保留退休金、仍可支薪及出獄後可復職等)，則會改採取對自身利益最大化的自私行為，即是瘋狂毆打市民。</blockquote><br />\n唔使用到理論解釋<br />\n簡單講，社會撒底不互信，官民不互信<br />\nsocial order 撒底消失<br />\n人人唔再用道理去解決紛爭，而係用最純粹既暴力去解決問題"},{"pid":"21628adf474dc112378720f7b6c9fc0225f442a2","tid":125221,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T13:46:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://blogs-images.forbes.com/markhughes/files/2016/04/PUNISHER-Daredevil-Season-2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblogs-images.forbes.com%2Fmarkhughes%2Ffiles%2F2016%2F04%2FPUNISHER-Daredevil-Season-2.png&h=a113b74a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n夜魔俠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似叫punisher<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2b3a5e172b0f0585e6336dadb5183e4275b4b3f","tid":125221,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T13:50:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>「道德危機」( Moral Hazard）理論<br />\n<br />